column2: Spatial transcriptomics (10x Visium) of human NSCLC lesions and non-involved tissue

We performed 10X Visium on consecutive 10 µm sections from 8 human NSCLC tumours (total 20 sections), 8 adjacent non-involved lung tissues (total 16 sections) and two healthy donors (total 4 sections)
